jenes.tutorials.problem2

Class PatternProblem

  • java.lang.Object
    • jenes.tutorials.problem2.PatternProblem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenerationEventListener<IntegerChromosome>

    public class PatternProblem
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenerationEventListener<IntegerChromosome>
    Tutorial showing how to extend GeneticAlgorithm and how to use the flexible and configurable breeding structure in Jenes. The problem consists in searching a pattern of integers with a given precision. Solutions flow through two different crossovers in parallel. Some are processed by a single point crossover, the other by a double point crossover. After solutions are mutated. This is the main class that specifies the problem.
